public abstract class BaseImmutableSymbolTable<Key,Value> extends Object implements ImmutableSymbolTable<Key,Value>
Abstract base class for implementing an immutable symbol table.

This class serves as a foundation for creating immutable symbol tables by providing the basic structure and functionality defined by the ImmutableSymbolTable interface. Concrete subclasses should extend this class to define specific implementations of an immutable symbol table.
